SAIF SURGICAL & SCIENTIFIC EQUIPMENT — Images Folder
=====================================================

Place your image files in this folder with the exact filenames listed below.
All images are referenced in index.html using these names.

REQUIRED IMAGE FILES:
---------------------
logo.png                  — Your business logo (PNG with transparent background)
hero-medical.jpg          — Homepage hero background (hospital/OT photo, 1920x1080px+)
category-surgical.jpg     — Surgical Instruments category card (600x400px)
category-laboratory.jpg   — Laboratory Equipment category card (600x400px)
category-scientific.jpg   — Scientific Tools category card (600x400px)
category-educational.jpg  — Educational Equipment category card (600x400px)
blog-ot-setup.jpg         — Blog post image: OT setup article (800x500px)
blog-equipment.jpg        — Blog post image: New equipment article (800x500px)
blog-tips.jpg             — Blog post image: Buying tips article (800x500px)

TIPS:
-----
- Use JPG for photos, PNG for logos/graphics
- Keep file sizes under 500KB each for fast loading
- Free stock photos: https://unsplash.com or https://pexels.com
  (search: hospital, laboratory, surgical, medical equipment)

